This Derivative Work contains significant modifications:
  - Complete reimplementation from Python to Rust
  - Direct perf_event_open syscall interface (no perf binary dependency)
  - Direct inotify syscall interface (no inotifywait binary dependency)
  - Static binary compilation for embedded Linux, Android, and Yocto targets
